      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[计算机网络] 基础知识</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="一次访问">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%b8%80%e6%ac%a1%e8%ae%bf%e9%97%ae"></a>
一次访问
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">你的软件
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">你的电脑网络配置
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">DNS：把域名翻译成 IP
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">网关/路由器：决定数据往哪走
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">运营商网络
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">目标服务器
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">目标服务器上的某个端口/服务
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="ip">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#ip"></a>
IP
</h2><p>机器的门牌号: <strong>IP 地址</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">192.168.1.50
</span></span></code></pre></div><h4 id="1-ipv4">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-ipv4"></a>
1. IPv4
</h4><p>IPv4 是现在最经典、最常见的 IP 地址格式
由 4 段数字组成，每段范围是 <code>0 ~ 255</code></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-29首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-29</p>]]>
